description: The first of two sites will opened on Thursday, while a second is scheduled to open on Monday.
title: Coronavirus: Dublin Airport Covid tests available at airport
title_page: Coronavirus: Dublin Airport Covid tests available at airport - BBC News
maintext: "We have been keen to provide testing at Dublin Airport for some time and the Government's recent decision to grant planning exemption, which we strongly welcome, will enable two testing facilities to open," he said.
